# Drooid – 6-Month Prototype Budget (with Founder Stipends)

---

## 1. Hardware Bill of Materials

| Component Group | Qty | Unit $ | Sub-total |
|-----------------|----:|-------:|----------:|
| Flight controllers (Pixhawk Mini) | 10 | 75 | 750 |
| Edge SBCs (Pi 5 / Orin-Nano) | 10 | 110 | 1 100 |
| Mesh radios (XBee SX 900) | 10 | 55 | 550 |
| Sensors (HD cam + gas/IR) | 10 | 65 | 650 |
| Motors + 4-in-1 ESCs | 40 / 10 | 11 / 8 | 520 |
| CF-Nylon printed frames | 10 | 12 | 120 |
| 2 S Li-ion packs | 10 | 12 | 120 |
| **Parts total** |  |  | **$3 810** |

