## 2. Non-Parts Spend (6 months)

| Item | 6-mo $ | Why it’s critical |
|------|-------:|-------------------|
| Newlab desks & printer resin | 8 000 | 24/7 print + indoor cage |
| AAIR corridor bookings (3 slots) | 4 000 | GPS-denied flight space |
| Liability & drone insurance | 3 000 | Required for test flights |
| Consumables, props, shipping | 3 000 | Keep builds unblocked |
| **Founder stipends** (2 × \$2.5 k/mo) | **30 000** | Housing, food—full-time focus |
| **Buffer / fixes** | 5 000 | Unforeseen swap-outs |
| **Non-parts subtotal** |  | **$53 000** |

---

## 3. All-in Prototype Budget  
**Hardware $3 810 + Ops/People $53 000 ≈ $56 800**  
(round to **$60 k** to stay safe)

---

## 4. Six-Month Milestones

| Month | Milestone |
|------:|-----------|
| **1** | Funds clear • parts ordered • insurance bound |
| **2** | Frames printed • bench test electronics |
| **3** | Indoor hover (Newlab cage) |
| **4** | GPS-denied nav test (AAIR slot #1) |
| **5** | Sensor integration flight (AAIR slot #2) |
| **6** | 10-unit swarm demo video + data package |

Outcome: working swarm in **180 days** on **≈ \$60 k** total spend.

